.. -*- rst -**

Change Log
==========

Release 0.3.5.2 - (November 20, 2017)
-------------------------------------
* Placage pypi.

Release 0.3.5.1 - (November 20, 2017)
-------------------------------------
* Allow wxPython 4 prereleases.

Release 0.3.5 - (November 19, 2017)
-----------------------------------
* Add Python 3 support.
* Require wxPython 4.
* Remove deprecated ez_setup.py.

Release 0.3.4 - (June 17, 2015)
-------------------------------
* Handle ESC properly.

Release 0.3.3 - (January 1, 2015)
---------------------------------
* Add support for QupZilla.
* Improve docs.
* Automatically build man page when building sdist.

Release 0.3.2 - (August 10, 2014)
---------------------------------
* Tidy up code.

Release 0.3.1 - (March 2, 2014)
-------------------------------
* Switch to PEP 440 version numbering.
* Include ez_setup.py.
* Assume optional config file is in standard XDG_CONFIG_HOME location.
* Access docutils programmatically when building man page.
* Include built man page in source package so docutils isn't needed for
  installation.

Release 0.03 - (January 08, 2013)
---------------------------------
* Add support for optional configuration file.

Release 0.02 - (April 11, 2012)
-------------------------------
* Add support for more browsers.
* Add man page.
* Use default icons.

Release 0.01 - (March 05, 2012)
-------------------------------
* First public release.
